    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/3880817/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            政治学说史（下卷）的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3240224">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3240224/" class="title-link">不多见的好书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3240224"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Eversint/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2790683-34.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Eversint/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Ubique</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-05"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-05 22:26:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3240224_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  先说下装帧问题。这本书用纸和印刷还是不错的。虽然很厚又没用线装，但阅读中没有脱页现象。唯一糟糕的是封面和封底，仿佛是漆面的，非常容易掉色。  这一本相较于上卷的翻译更为顺畅，语气和句式的拿捏也更为老练，译名的处理也更为统一且恰当。但是erastianism虽然在pp127中...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3240224/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">20有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3240224_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3240224_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4632118">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4632118/" class="title-link">无题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4632118"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/13118951/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u13118951-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/13118951/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Gino</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-15"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-15 12:46:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4632118_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  和麦克里兰的《西方政治思想史》相比，萨拜因的上下两卷更侧重于反映某一政治思想的时代背景、演变过程、思想渊源；更强调各思想家之间的某种“勾连”（邓正来爱用这词儿）。 以往理解错误或偏颇的地方在这本书中得到纠正，同时又引发了许多新的思考和随之而来的新问题。挺好！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4632118/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4632118_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4632118_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










